e":"2019-12-30T02:09:44.000Z","msg":"墊底有寫，睇番份保險就知<br />\n<br />\n你個case要睇多少少，因為<br />\n<br />\n好似睇到你車用爸爸名出，咁要睇埋有無加你名<br />\n保單通常有寫 inexperience driver 同unnamed driver 個墊底會貴d<br />\n<br />\n墊底係唔想d人乜野小事都走去claim"},{"pid":"26b6a7d365d36a05f87d590cbd76a8ac7b000e40","tid":1802990,"uid":46266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec3f563fb4fe55da1a38927bb8b9279d9feb49b7","tid":1802990,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fba0bffd808130dab1339f6a62a092c2dd6d5a3d","tid":1802990,"uid":46266,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"607ec7ebeaa758aca747d137b7ba6488c5de4275","tid":1802990,"uid":4392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T02:02:49.000Z","msg":"冇最尾和解左冇claim到保險...<br />\n<br />\nbtw 你0 ncb 三保要$3000? 牌齡好新?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T02:06:14.000Z","msg":"20年牌爸爸名，0 ncb 。<br />\n我以為$3000已經好平。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T02:08:30.000Z","msg":"0 NCB 3K都好似有少少貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大cc車?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T02:10:00.000Z","msg":"2000。<br />\n唔係跑車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好誤會<br />\n不過係絕版車"},{"pid":"0a456830c03190eb823178a2d25f5326b1c2c76a","tid":1802990,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26b6a7d365d36a05f87d590cbd76a8ac7b000e40","tid":1802990,"uid":46266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec3f563fb4fe55da1a38927bb8b9279d9feb49b7","tid":1802990,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fba0bffd808130dab1339f6a62a092c2dd6d5a3d","tid":1802990,"uid":46266,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T02:06:14.000Z","msg":"20年牌爸爸名，0 ncb 。<br />\n我以為$3000已經好平。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T02:08:30.000Z","msg":"0 NCB 3K都好似有少少貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"